A cyberpunk-style illustration of a glowing neon blue database cylinder floating in a dark digital void, connected by pulsing electric streams to multiple floating translucent comment bubbles that spiral around it like satellites. The bubbles contain abstract geometric patterns representing data flow. Below, a sleek chrome robotic hand reaches up, fingers extended, catching streams of luminous cyan and magenta particles that flow between the bubbles and database. The background features a rain-soaked cityscape with towering servers disguised as skyscrapers, their windows flickering with cascading code patterns. Purple and electric blue fog rolls through the scene, with holographic hexagonal grids floating in the atmosphere. The overall mood is mysterious yet technologically sophisticated, emphasizing the concept of custom-built digital infrastructure and data flowing through a self-controlled system.
